data.description: Don’t miss this opportunity! Single-story, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage home. High ceilings, ceiling fans, lots of windows and natural daylight, including a large bay-window in the living room and sliding glass doors in the family room, leading to a large, private back yard. The kitchen features, microwave, five burner gas stove, island with additional storage, and a reverse osmosis drinking water system. All appliances included. Everything stays, even refrigerator, washer and dryer. Water softener, solar panels, and new water heater. Conveniently located near lots of shopping and dining.
